These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apricot, cranberry, spinach
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, dancer, engineer, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, nigerian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, climbing, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 3. the engineer is on the right of the dancer##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 5. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 6. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the teacher##1
 9. the person drinking cola is the person eating cranberry##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
11. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
12. the engineer is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
13. the italian is on the right of the dancer##1
14. the brazilian is on the far left##1
15. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |       3       |        4        |
| Beverage      | sprite    | mirinda        | cola | 7up     |
| Food          | asparagus    | apricot  | cranberry     | spinach          |
| Job           | dancer | engineer     | teacher    | police-officer |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | italian    | nigerian       | dutch          |
| Sport         | cricket  | climbing | tennis       | baseball         |

