.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
There 4 different types of food: avocado, grapefruit, potato, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, puzzles, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, pilot, software-developer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, biathlon, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is the scientist##1
 2. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
11. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the chef is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is skiing##2
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
14. the chef is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | hot-chocolate    | juice        | fanta         |
| Food       | potato   | grapefruit      | grapes       | avocado        |
| Hobby      | reading | puzzles | cooking  | woodworking |
| Job        | scientist  | pilot   | chef   | software-developer     |
| Sport      | rugby | skiing    | biathlon | lacrosse       |

