.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, radish, pear, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, chess, reading, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, sports, family, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, punk, dubstep, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, basketball, skiing, surfing
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the person eating peas is the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
 6. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person watching family movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 8. the person watching action movies is the fan of punk##1
 9. the person watching action movies is the person watching action movies##1
10. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
11. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
12. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
13. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | broccoli       | radish     | pear    | peas      |
| Hobby         | hiking    | video-games  | reading  | chess   |
| Movie-Genre   | sports        | family    | spy  | action |
| Music-Genre   | indie          | dubstep     | disco    | punk   |
| Sport         | surfing | basketball | cycling | skiing    |

