.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, writer, chef, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, crime, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, gospel, r&b, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, colombian, brazilian, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, weightlifting, ice-hockey
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the pilot##2
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 3. the scientist is on the left of the colombian##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 6. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the chef is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the chef is the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the brazilian is the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
12. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the writer##5
13. the fan of metal is between the pilot and the fan of r&b##2
14. the person who's sport is golf is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | pilot | writer | scientist | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | time-travel   | sports  | superhero   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | metal  | r&b       | trance        |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | italian  | indonesian      | colombian     |
| Sport         | golf | weightlifting | ice-hockey     | surfing     |

