.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, superhero, thriller, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, d&b, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, japanese, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: fish, bird, frog, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, van, boat
 1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 2. the japanese is in an even position##4
 3. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
 4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the pakistani##1
 6. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the van and the fan of reggae##2
 9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
11. the indonesian is the person watching thriller movies##1
12. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
13. the person watching superhero movies is between the fan of trance and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | superhero    | thriller | spy |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | jazz   | trance    | reggae    |
| Nationality   | indian | japanese | indonesian | pakistani   |
| Pet           | frog   | fish     | bird     | snake        |
| Transport     | boat     | van  | snowmobile    | skateboard    |

