 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 5. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of house##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the thai##1
