 9. the person watching drama movies is the malaysian##1
10. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the thai##1
11. the argentine is the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
14. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
15. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
16. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is singing##1

