 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the polish##3
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the mexican is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person driving the motorbike##2
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
 8. the mexican is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 9. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
10. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
