The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, western, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, tram, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating kiwi is the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person eating kiwi and the chef##2
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the analyst is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating plum is between the person watching western movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
10. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
11. the accountant is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
